      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="1fa13874b45198df" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Combat: A basilisk bites like a snake, inflicting 5 points of damage and injecting a poison that moves the target one step down the damage track if they fail a Might defense roll.</source>
