      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="78018f7bd0920b7b" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>The basilisk can spit its poison up to short range, inflicting 1 point of damage and moving the target one step down the damage track if they fail a Might defense roll.</source>
